title: 5V DC 2000mA Regulated Power Supply 1.35mm X 3.5mm Tip, Extra Power
description:
5VDC 2000mA (2A) Regulated Power Supply 1.35mm X 3.5mm Tip, Extra Power
AC input voltage            100-240VAC 50/60Hz
 
 Output Voltage              5V DC (Regulated & Filterer) 

 Amp                             2A
 
 Plug Tip size                  3.5mm (Out Side), 1.35mm (inside Hole) (see Photo)
 
 Working temperature    0-35℃@100%,50℃@70% load
 
 Safety standards              CE, CCCs&e;




 
 
 
Features:
 
 Regulated and filterer output protects your electronic devices from over voltage damages, and increase life of electronic circuits and products you are using with.
 
 This Power supply is CE and CCCs&e; certified and approved.
 
 Perfect for any CCTV Cameras and electronic products...
 
 Use it with For Security Cameras, etc. (Extra power for LED cameras)
 
 3 oz
 
 Power Red LED
 
 Support Infra-Red Cameras
